&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with distributed computing tools such as queues, load balancers, fail over, automatic configuration and optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SQL: In particular GCP BigQuery dialect&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
