&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Principal Product Manager, CTV&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Principal Product Manager, CTV&lt;/strong&gt; will play a key role in shaping the next phase of mediasmart’s CTV platform, advertiser offering, and &lt;strong&gt;North America growth strategy.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
