&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity for someone who understands both branding and performance use cases within the CTV ecosystem and is passionate about helping build and scale innovative advertising solutions across connected devices and screens.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
