&lt;li&gt;Go further. Be an example for others. Set the bar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong ownership of the role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Love what we do. Love our work with passion and respect.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do good and do well. Our work matters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are absolutely devoted to our customers and to building the best advertising technology company out there. We work hard and never forget to have fun in the process.&lt;/p&gt;
